AC 24; Fort +15, Ref +18, Will +14; +1 status to all saves vs. magic
HP 110; Immunities disease, paralyzed, poison, precision, sleep; Resistances all 5
(except force, ghost touch, or negative; double resistance vs. non-magical)
Speed fly 40 feet
