as a shield archon (Bestiary 29).
Retributive Strike [reaction] A star archon can also make a Retributive Strike by throwing
its starknife, and the enemy and ally can be within 60 feet instead of 15 feet.
Speed 35 feet, fly 75 feet
Melee [one-action] returning starknife +38 (agile, deadly 1d8, finesse, good, magical, reach
10 feet, versatile S), Damage 3d4+16 piercing plus 2d6 good and
