Maximum Duration 6 rounds; Stage 1 1d6 poison damage and
enfeebled 1 (1 round); Stage 2 As stage 1; Stage 3 1d6 poison
damage and enfeebled 2 (1 round). See Pathfinder Bestiary 51
for full details on this alchemical poison.
Call to Blood[two-actions] (enchantment, mental, occult) Each caligni within 30 feet
gains a +2 status bonus to attack rolls against flat-footed creatures.
This bonus lasts for 1 minute.
Soul Harvest (necromancy) The caligni slayer deals an additional 2d6
negative damage to flat-footed creatures.
