Appendix
HELLFIRE
Stinking, sulfurous hellfire is infused
with evil. Hellfire always deals a
combination of fire damage and evil
damage, though the specific ratio
depends on the hellfire’s origin. Certain
types of hellfire can impose other
effects on creatures as well, such as
sapping their strength or memories.
SARGLAGON CREATURE 8
