HAMATULA TREASURES
Perhaps because hamatulas exist to
guard the riches of archdevils, infernal
dukes, and queens of the night, they
find themselves drawn to wealth.
Though they despise summoners who
pull them away from their assigned
duties, hamatulas use their servitude
as an opportunity to collect treasures
and wealth that they can offer to their
lords upon their return. Treasures that
are painful or dangerous to handle are
among their favorite prizes.
Str +7, Dex +6, Con +5, Int +1, Wis +5, Cha +4
