THE MALEBRANCHE
Every 5,000 years, the mightiest
cornugon becomes a malebranche,
a quasi-deity below infernal dukes.
Scholars on Golarion currently know
of 12 active malebranche, and while
each is unique, all share the goal of
conquering the Material Plane.
