Capsize [one-action] (attack) The drake tries to capsize an adjacent aquatic vessel of its size or
smaller. The drake must succeed at an Athletics check with a DC of 25 (reduced by 5 for each
size smaller the vessel is than the drake) or the pilot’s Sailing Lore DC, whichever is higher.
