DIVERSE ELEMENTALS
The Elemental Planes are more
than expanses of sky, rock, fire,
and ocean. Clouds of fog, dust, and
storms float through the Plane of Air.
The Plane of Earth includes verdant
groves, shining metal and crystal,
and irradiated wastelands. The Plane
of Fire features magma, suffocating
smoke, and radiant firelight. Amid the
endless sea of the Plane of Water are
pockets of ooze and brine, plus the
otherworldly environs of the deep.
Elemental, Air
Some elementals embody aspects of air such as smoke, lightning, and fog.
SPARK BAT
Spark bats congregate around volatile weather in the Plane of Air.
SPARK BAT CREATURE 2
N TINY AIR ELEMENTAL
Perception +7; darkvision
Skills Acrobatics +9, Stealth +9
Str +0, Dex +3, Con +1, Int –4, Wis +1, Cha +0
