bolt of lightning that crashes with deafening thunder. The living thunderclap makes
a lightning bolt Strike that deals 1d12 electricity damage. If it hits, the target and any
creatures within a 15-foot emanation around the target take 2d6 sonic damage and
must attempt a DC 18 basic Fortitude save. Any creature that fails its save is also
