emanation must attempt a DC 30 Will save to resist becoming fascinated by
the melody on the wind. A creature that succeeds at its save is temporarily
immune for 24 hours.
Critical Success The creature is unaffected.
Success The creature is fascinated for 1 round.
Failure The creature is fascinated for 1d4 rounds.
Swiftness The melody on the wind’s movement doesn’t trigger reactions.
