ELEMENTAL WYRMS
The icewyrm is the most widely
encountered elemental wyrm, but
others exist as well, including the
blazing firewyrm, the sleek but
somewhat smaller sparkwyrm, and
the largest of them all, the immense
and acidic sludgewyrm.
move with crunching strides, their bodies constantly sloshing and sloughing off
shards of ice. Because of their ability to refreeze, blizzardborn can travel into warmer
environments safely, though they tend to look more like slush in these areas.
