Stealth +13 (+15 in forests), Survival +13
Str +5, Dex +5, Con +4, Int +2, Wis +3, Cha +1
Items hide armor, +1 composite longbow (20 arrows),
shortsword
AC 24; Fort +17, Ref +14, Will +13
HP 120
Catch Rock[reaction]
