Icy Demise (arcane, cold, evocation) When an ice golem
is destroyed, its body explodes in a blast of frigid air
and razor-sharp ice, dealing 2d6 slashing damage
and 2d6 cold damage to creatures in a 20-foot
emanation, with a DC 19 basic Reflex save.
