AC 28; Fort +15, Ref +18, Will +21; +1 status to all
saves vs. magic (+2 vs. divine magic)
HP 155; Immunities death effects, disease,
poison; Resistances fire 10, negative 10
Positive Energy Affinity Positive healing
effects always heal the jyoti for the
maximum amount. It doesn’t gain the
automatic Hit Points or temporary Hit
Points from being on a plane with the
positive planar essence.
