within 30 feet that has the same minimum size. Once the korred enters the stone, they
instantly know the rough locations of other sufficiently large stones within 30 feet.
They can exit from the original stone, if they prefer. They can’t carry extradimensional
spaces with them when they Stone Stride; if the korred attempts to do so, Stone
Stride fails.
