HP 50; Immunities bleed, death effects, disease, doomed, drained,
fatigued, healing, mental, necromancy, nonlethal attacks, paralyzed,
poison, sickened, unconscious; Weaknesses bludgeoning 5
Speed 25 feet
Melee [one-action] jaws +8 (agile, finesse), Damage 1d10+3 piercing plus
necrophidic paralysis
