clattering in a hypnotic rhythm. Each creature that witnesses
the dance must attempt a DC 18 Will save.
Critical Success The creature is unaffected and is
temporarily immune for 24 hours.
Success The creature is unnerved by the swaying
and becomes flat-footed until the end of the
necrophidius’s next turn.
Failure The creature is distracted by the
swaying, becoming stunned 1. After
it recovers, it is flat-footed until the
end of the necrophidius’s next turn.
Critical Failure As failure, but
stunned 3.
