Change Shape [one-action] (concentrate, polymorph, primal, transmutation) The onidoshi takes on
the appearance of an ogre. This doesn’t change their Speed or Strike attack and damage.
ICE YAI
Ice yai combine the brutality of frost giants with the grace of martial artists. More
than any other oni, ice yai delight not in the pleasures of the flesh, but in flesh
itself—rather than indulging in oft-destructive mortal vices like drink or lust, ice
yai pursue physical perfection, reveling in the process of turning their bodies into
powerful fighting machines.
