against the peluda; Effect The peluda shifts their position and
makes a quill Strike against the attacking creature. This Strike
doesn’t count toward the peluda’s multiple attack penalty, and
the peluda’s multiple attack penalty doesn’t apply to this Strike.
Speed 30 feet, swim 30 feet
Melee [one-action] jaws +23 (reach 10 feet), Damage 2d12+13 piercing
