CHERNOBUE
The chernobue infects all creatures it encounters
with itself, spreading pain and calamity wherever it
flops and writhes. It sheds ruin and sups on anguish,
but a chernobue can sometimes be persuaded to pause
for a few moments of conversation if its partner in
discourse can keep its attention by providing
enough atrocious details. Resembling a
tumor-like growth of oily blackness, this
vile monstrosity has numerous muscular
tentacles, a single glaring baleful eye, and a drooling, toothy maw
in the middle of its body.
