Abyss, thulgants amuse themselves with a variety of diversions, such as maintaining
galleries of petrified mortals or building massive, hive-like lairs filled with enslaved
minions. Each of these qlippoth is a horrific tangle of limbs, with spiderlike legs,
writhing tentacles emerging from the top of its head, and three scorpion-like stingers.
