Boneshatter [reaction] Trigger The ravener husk takes any amount of bludgeoning damage;
Effect The ravener’s brittle bones shatter, spraying bone shards everywhere. Every
creature within a 10-foot emanation of the ravener husk takes 7d6 piercing damage
