and they rise as skeletons. The bone prophet can raise one Large creature
as a skeletal giant or up to three Medium creatures as skeletal champions;
the equipment and attacks might be different depending on the corpses’
possessions (Bestiary 298). These skeletons have the minion trait and
are under the bone prophet’s control; the bone prophet can give all
these minions the same command with a single action that has
the concentrate trait. Any skeletal minions that still
remain after 10 minutes crumble to dust.
