CAVERN TROLL
Insatiable scavengers stalking the eternal gloom
of the Darklands, cavern trolls consume all in
their path—even rocks and minerals when more
nourishing sustenance is scarce. These rocky
goliaths can tunnel through stone with their
iron-sharp claws.
