HP 190, regeneration 25 (deactivated by acid or fire); Weaknesses fire 10
Head Regrowth A two-headed troll’s regeneration can regrow a severed head. After
regaining Hit Points from regeneration, the two-headed troll attempts a DC 10 flat
check. On a success, the missing head is fully restored. If a two-headed troll
loses their last remaining head, they die immediately.
