VELSTRACS ON GOLARION
Velstracs are most often
encountered in the shadowy realm
of Nidal, where the state worship
of Zon-Kuthon is rigidly enforced.
Indeed, many velstracs are created
from the souls of Joyful Things,
devotees of Zon-Kuthon who have
had their limbs amputated to focus
their minds on the veneration of
pain, sacrifice, and torment.
