a DC 26 Fortitude save or become drained 1. It recovers after it has been out of the
aura for 1 minute. This drained condition value is cumulative with the drained value
caused by drain life, but not with multiple draining presence auras. A creature
that succeeds at its save is temporarily immune to draining presence for 24 hours.
