Absorb Wraith [two-actions] The dread wraith extends its hand toward
another wraith creature within 100 feet. The target wraith
dissolves and streaks toward the dread wraith in a straight
line, dealing 6d10 negative damage to each creature along the
line (DC 28 basic Fortitude save). The dread wraith absorbs the
essence of the target wraith, becoming quickened and gaining a
+10-foot status bonus to its fly Speed for a number of rounds
equal to the level of the absorbed wraith. It can use its
extra action only to Fly or Strike. An unwilling target can
attempt a DC 28 Will save to resist being absorbed.
