Rulebook
More Monsters,
More Mayhem!
More than 300 menacing monsters and fearsome foes await within this
compendium of creatures from the world of Pathfinder! From classic adversaries
like giants, dragons, and the jabberwock to potential allies and servants suitable
for summoners of every alignment, this must-have expansion to the Pathfinder
Bestiary seethes with enemies to challenge characters of any level.
paizo.com/pathfinder Printed in China. 